包装</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">0.2</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">中粮包装</span><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">(00906)</span></td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">7.13（0%）</td></tr><tr><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">石油与天然气</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">0</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">中国海洋石油</span><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">(00883)</span></td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">18.48（-0.2%）</td></tr><tr><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">电讯业</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">0</td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">中国移动</span><span style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle;\">(00941)</span></td><td style=\"vertical-align: middle; border: 1px solid#999; padding: 7px 0;\">84.3（1%）</td></tr></table></div>",
